Package: BioClockR
Title: Biological Age Estimation from Routine Clinical Biomarkers
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Naresh", "Gumala",
           email = "naresh.gumala@n2cloudtech.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Implements the PhenoAge biological age algorithm (Levine et al., 2018)
    using nine routine clinical blood biomarkers from NHANES 2015-2020.
    Provides functions to compute biological age, age acceleration, survival
    validation using the NHANES public-use linked mortality file, and
    cross-validation against GEO gene expression aging signatures.
    Includes a Shiny web application for interactive biological age estimation.
